I have always been passionate about advancing the state of generative AI and building intelligent, scalable AI-driven products that deliver real user outcomes. I envision myself contributing my talent to the furthering of your mission to build innovative AI solutions that bridge cutting-edge research and production-grade engineering. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration — I look forward to connecting!

